AOC : account of chart code
International Financial Reporting Standards

1xx – Assets
  1.1 – Cash and Cash Equivalents
  1.2 – Financial Assets
  1.3 – Trade Receivables
  1.4 – Inventories
  1.5 – Property, Plant & Equipment
  1.6 – Intangible Assets
  1.7 – Right of Use Assets

2xx – Liabilities
  2.1 – Trade Payables
  2.2 – Borrowings
  2.3 – Lease Liabilities
  2.4 – Deferred Tax Liabilities

3xx – Equity
  3.1 – Share Capital
  3.2 – Retained Earnings
  3.3 – Other Equity Items

4xx – Revenue
  4.1 – Sales Revenue
  4.2 – Service Revenue

5xx – Expenses
  5.1 – Cost of Sales
  5.2 – Operating Expenses
  5.3 – Depreciation / Amortization
  5.4 – Finance Cost
